&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a class="ext-link" href="http://trac.okfn.org/ticket/933"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;http://trac.okfn.org/ticket/933&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
